&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staff Nurse - Band 5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ward B4B&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12 Hour Shifts - Full/Part Time Posts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Permanent &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome highly motivated applicants, who are looking for a challenge and to join our dynamic and diverse team. Our acute surgical ward specialising in colorectal and general surgery, aims to provide a high quality effective service to all patients, encompassing the trusts vison and values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A role with the ward offers a great opportunity to gain broad acute experience and develop your personal and professional confidence in supporting a wide range of patients of differing levels of dependency. There are plenty of learning opportunities and a competency package is offered to help develop knowledge, skills and confidence surrounding all aspects of this specialist area. Particular advantage with Clinical Nurse Specialist based on the ward supporting both team and patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Natalie Hamilton Ext 2665&lt;/p&gt;
